    <h1>
      <a href="https://blog.prosody.im/prosody-0-10-2-security-release/">Prosody 0.10.2 and 0.9.14 Security Release</a>
    </h1>
    <div class="callout small">
      <small>
        <div style="float:right;width:50%;text-align:right">
